author: rhuijben
msg: Following up on r1337604, report a commit error on all obstructed commit
targets instead of just symlink changes.
Note that the old behavior could result in checking the commit status in a
different working copy, in case a node is obstructed by another working copy.
This allows removing more processing from libsvn_wc's commit helper function.
(svn_wc_notify_action_t): Add notification for obstruction, to help gui
Use result pool for lock tokens.
